dewox - An RAD [de]momaker inspired by [W]erkkzeug for [O]penGL & Linu[x]

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 REQUIREMENTS
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
OS           : Linux
Compiler     : gcc or clang
Dependencies : OpenGL, OpenAL, GLUT, scons

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 INSTALLATION
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
It's quite simple once you get all the requirements worked correctly.
Just type following command, then you can compile it.

	scons

If you want to configure the compilation, type 'scons -h' for more details.

